'''2020年共和党全国代表大会'''是2020年8月24日至27日间[[美国共和党|美国共和党]]举行的[[共和党全国代表大会|总统提名大会]]，该大会决定[[2020年美国总统大选|2020年美国总统大选]]中该党的总统和副总统候选人。<ref>{{cite news|author=WCNC Staff|url=https://www.wcnc.com/article/news/politics/2020-republican-national-convention-dates-announced/275-599687656|title=WCNC: 2020 Republican National Convention dates announced|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181002132338/https://www.wcnc.com/article/news/politics/2020-republican-national-convention-dates-announced/275-599687656|archivedate=2018-10-02|date=October 1, 2018|accessdate=2020-10-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>由于美国[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|2019冠状病毒病疫情]]，<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/07/23/us/politics/jacksonville-rnc.html |title=Trump Abruptly Cancels Republican Convention in Florida: 'It's Not the Right Time' |first1=Maggie |last1=Haberman |first2=Patricia |last2=Mazzei |first3=Annie |last3=Karni |work=New York Times |date=July 23, 2020 |access-date=July 24, 2020 |archive-date=2020-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200724054313/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/07/23/us/politics/jacksonville-rnc.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>此次大会取消了传统的大型集会，举办地是[[北卡罗来纳州|北卡罗来纳州]][[夏洛特|夏洛特]]的{{le|夏洛特会议中心|Charlotte Convention Center}}和[[华盛顿特区|华盛顿特区]]的[[安德鲁·梅隆礼堂|安德鲁·梅隆礼堂]]等场馆。大会再次提名了现任总统[[唐纳德·特朗普|唐纳德·特朗普]]总统和副总统[[迈克·彭斯|迈克·彭斯]]为总统候选人。8月27日，中国盲人人权辩护律师[[陈光诚|陈光诚]]出席此次大会并在安德鲁·梅隆礼堂发表演讲，称[[中共|中共]]是人类的公敌，对特朗普表示支持。<ref>{{cite news |author1=Owen Churchill |title=Chinese dissident Chen Guangcheng to speak at Republican National Convention to endorse Trump for re-election |url=https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3099008/chinese-dissident-chen-guangcheng-speak-republican-national-convention |accessdate=2020-08-27 |work=South China Morning Post |date=2020-08-27 |location=Washington, DC |archive-date=2021-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107014935/https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3099008/chinese-dissident-chen-guangcheng-speak-republican-national-convention |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Dreisbach |first1=Tom |title=RNC Speaker Facing Federal Charges Of Insider Trading |url=https://www.npr.org/2020/08/25/905953942/rnc-speaker-facing-federal-charges-of-insider-trading |website=NPR.org |accessdate=27 August 2020 |language=en |date=25 August 2020 |archive-date=2020-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200826144329/https://www.npr.org/2020/08/25/905953942/rnc-speaker-facing-federal-charges-of-insider-trading |dead-url=no }}</ref>

